  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the contamination rate of the parents cell phone in
      a newborn intensive care setting and identify the types of bacteria contaminating the cell
      phone as well as evaluating the effectiveness of an antimicrobial gel in reducing the
      transmission of bacteria from the cell phone to the parents hands.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
